Microwave chocolate in large microwaveable bowl on HIGH 2 min. or until chocolate is almost melted, stirring every 30 sec. Stir until chocolate is completely melted. Add peanut butter; stir until well blended. Cool to room temperature. Gently stir in whipped topping. Refrigerate 2 hours. Scoop truffle mixture with melon baller or teaspoon, then roll into 1-inch balls. Roll in suggested coatings. Store in tightly covered container in refrigerator.